# Evolution runs: TRACK the small artifacts (ledger, per-gen heuristics/rules,
# failure reports, attempts.md, SUMMARY.md) but NOT the huge prepared-brain
# pickle (~2 GB each). (Also covered by the global *.pkl above; listed here too
# for clarity since runs/ is otherwise tracked.)
proofreader_evolve/runs/**/prepared_*.pkl

